OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FThe Jordan International Search and
OL,8,FRescue Team pulled out the child
OL,9,Fbefore taking him to hospital.
OL,11,FCredit: Jordan Civil Defence
OL,13,FA three-year-old was rescued after
OL,14,Fbeing trapped under rubble for six
OL,15,Fdays following the Venezuela
OL,16,Fearthquakes.
OL,18,FJordan International Search and Rescue
OL,19,FTeam pulled Kleiber Moran out from
OL,20,Funder a house in the capital Caracas
OL,21,Fafter the building collapsed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
