OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782845288
OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FThe toddler was found alive and after
OL,8,Freceiving first aid was taken to the
OL,9,Fnearest hospital.
OL,11,FThe Public Security Directorate said
OL,12,Fhis vital signs were good.
OL,14,FThe magnitude 7.2 and 7.5 quakes last
OL,15,Fweek destroyed more than 770
OL,16,Fbuildings, trapping people inside.
OL,18,FMore than 1,700 have been killed and
OL,19,Fas many as 50,000 are still missing,
OL,20,Faccording to authorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
