PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782845288
OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FRelief organisations say the first 72
OL,8,Fhours after a natural disaster is the
OL,9,Fmost crucial period for rescues,
OL,10,Fthough people can still survive if
OL,11,Fthey have access to food and water.
OL,13,FVenezuelan merchant Grian Serrano has
OL,14,Fsurvived two of the country's natural
OL,15,Fdisasters: the 1999 mudslides and the
OL,16,Ftwo recent earthquakes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
