CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782845288
OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FHe, his eight-year-old son, and his
OL,8,Fmother were buried beneath rubble and
OL,9,Ftwisted steel after the earthquake
OL,10,Fcaused their eight-storey apartment
OL,11,Fhome in Caraballeda to collapse on top
OL,12,Fof them.
OL,14,FAfter clawing through debris Serrano
OL,15,Fmanaged to save the three of them in
OL,16,Fwhat he called "a miracle from God".
OL,26,@xD@POUxD@cO]
