OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782845288
OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FThe government reported 600
OL,8,Faftershocks since the quakes on
OL,9,FWednesday, including one which the
OL,10,FUnited States Geological Survey
OL,11,Fmeasured as 4.6 magnitude.
OL,13,FConcepcion Hernandez, who was
OL,14,Fevacuating her apartment in the Chacao
OL,15,Fmunicipality of Caracas, said: "I
OL,16,Fdon't know when we'll have a moment of
OL,17,Ftrue peace."
OL,19,FAttention has now also turned to the
OL,20,Fcountry's humanitarian crisis.
OL,26,@uD@IrwuD@PrpwD@`OUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
