CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782845288
OL,3,CToddler saved from rubble as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for Venezuela earthquake
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FPolice and military officers on Monday
OL,8,Fhave handed out cans of tuna and
OL,9,Fcrackers to displaced people in the
OL,10,Fhardest-hit state La Guaira.
OL,12,FJorge Rodriguez, the leader of the
OL,13,FVenezuelan National Assembly, said
OL,14,Felectricity had been restored to 90%
OL,15,Fof La Guaira.
OL,17,FHe said rescue teams are continuing to
OL,18,Fsearch and 15 temporary displacement
OL,19,Fcamps have been set up.
